---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Tanya Ortega">
  <section style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 56px 24px;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 56px; line-height: 1.05;">
      About Me
    </h1>

    <div style="max-width: 72ch;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 14px; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.92;">
        I am a data science professional with a background in analytics, K-12 special education teaching, and applied machine learning. I recently completed my Master of Data Science at the University of San Diego, graduating with a <strong>3.94 GPA</strong>.
      </p>

    <div
      style="
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 26px;
      "
    >
      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 20px;">What I Do</h2>
        <p style="margin:0; line-height: 1.7; opacity: .92;">
          I work across data analysis and applied machine learning, building reproducible workflows, dashboards, and reports that support operational, business, and policy-driven decision making.
          <br /><br />
          My experience includes ETL pipelines, data cleaning, forecasting, and classification modeling across education, healthcare, and transportation data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 20px;">Academic Recognition</h2>
        <p style="margin:0; line-height: 1.7; opacity: .92;">
          I was nominated for the University of San Diego’s <strong>Alcalá 100 Award</strong>, which recognizes graduating students for exceptional academic achievement, leadership, and impact within the university community.
          <br /><br />
          This nomination was submitted by faculty in recognition of my contributions, professionalism, and impact within the Applied Data Science and Applied Artificial Intelligence programs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 20px;">Education</h2>
        <p style="margin:0; line-height: 1.7; opacity: .92;">
          <strong>Master of Data Science</strong> — University of San Diego<br />
          GPA: 3.94
          <br /><br />
          <strong>Bachelor of Arts in Psychology</strong> — California State University, Channel Islands
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px; font-size: 20px;">Technical Toolkit</h2>
        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;">
          <span class="pill">Python</span>
          <span class="pill">SQL</span>
          <span class="pill">ETL</span>
          <span class="pill">Data Cleaning</span>
          <span class="pill">Machine Learning</span>
          <span class="pill">Time Series Forecasting</span>
          <span class="pill">Dashboards</span>
          <span class="pill">Streamlit</span>
          <span class="pill">Excel</span>
          <span class="pill">Technical Documentation</span>
          <span class="pill">GitHub</span>
          <span class="pill">Public Datasets</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

